Subject: RE: [VB] How To Tell Original Hubcaps?

  OE Vdub in Colorado has NEW genuine VW (domed) hubcaps. On the early
original ones they were 2 piece. I do not know what year this changed to the
one piece. I have both styles and cases of hubcaps and have yet to sort them
out to see. It seems that on old (OG) ones I have the chrome will polish out
real nice and will not be as pitted from rust as old repos. 
  Maybe a good BBB game pick out the og hubcap contest `

